title: Emitever Double Sided Tape, Double Sided Tape Heavy Duty Mounting Tape, 23 FT*0.6 Inch Double Sided Sticky Tape, Strong Adhesive Waterproof Foam Tape for Automotive, Home Decor
features: Double Sided Tape Heavy Duty: 90lb per inch longitudinally. 23ft length, 0.6inch width double sided tape is a Must-Have in Your Household. It can be used to install large and heavy tools, car paint, plastic, glass, wood, metal and ceramic tiles and other Smooth surface, (Not for fabric). No more take time to drill or screw to decorate your home and office.

Easy to remove without residue: Virtually invisible double sided tape keeps surfaces smooth. This is a mess-free alternative to ordinary gluish tapes, hammers, nails, screws, and other stuff you use to attach things to other objects. Warm Tips: We don't suggest using it on the flimsy wall, avoid causing the surface of the wall to fall off.

Strong Ductility: The strong double sided adhesive tape can be extended to meet your requirement, and will not break even if it is stretched several times longer. The stickiness is still very strong. (Note: It is better to use more strips for more heavy items)

Waterproof and Temperature Resistance: Consists of a durable acrylic adhesive with viscoelastic properties, making the adhesive tape good for outdoors or bathroom. For example, it will not fall off if it is attached to the car window in summer or winter. Perfect to use on LED strip mounting, moldings, door edge, bodyside moldings.

Easy To Use: This double sided mounting tape is easy to install, Simply peel and stick it to the surface of the object. it bonds quickly and securely when it’s fully compressed. No gluing, No heating, No screwing, and No wall damage. Foam tape can be extended to suit your needs. Any questions, please feel free to contact us, we will provide you with a satisfactory reply within 24 hours. (Tips: The initial usage temperature for the tape is 10 ℃ or above. When the temperature is below 10℃, you can use a hairdryer to heat the surface of the tape before use for better adhesion.)

Why choose Emitever double sided tape? Acrylic Foam Tape Different from traditional PE foam tape. This heavy duty tape is black, double-coated adhesive tape with an acrylic foam core, offers excellent shear strength, conformability, adhesion, and temperature resistance. It can replace mechanical fasteners or liquid adhesives in general, eliminate drilling, grinding, refinishing, screwing, welding and clean-up. Keeping it simple and beautiful, also greatly improves your work efficiency. Why choose Emitever double sided tape? Flexibility & Ductility The viscoelastic properties of acrylic adhesive and more than 30% elongation give the tape strong toughness and elasticity. Can be freely cut and twisted as your needs without break. Why choose Emitever double sided tape? Seal & Waterproof The viscoelasticity and 100% closed-cell foam structure of tape create a permanent seal against water, moisture, and environment erosion by offering better gap-filling capabilities. You can use it in bathrooms, kitchens, and other wet environments. Also, be used to bond metals to anti-rust. Why choose Emitever double sided tape? Temperature Resistance This two-sided tape is UV and temperature stable, which can maintain good stickiness under 150℉ heat to -40℉ cold. Excellent temperature resistance of 450°F for up to 4 hours. Suitable for outdoor use. For example, it will not fall off if it is attached to the car window in summer or winter. Heavy Duty Adhesive Tape The longer the time, the stronger the stickness Emitever tape is a proven alternative to mechanical fasteners. Its weight capacity is 4lb per inch, the excellent performance can be competent for any light to heavy duty application. This tapes is pressure-sensitive adhesives, it is extremely durable and the stickiness will gradually increase over time and reaches a maximum after 72 hours. When the tape is used on wallpaper, fabrics, textured walls, brick, and other rough and porous surfaces, its stickiness is also greatly reduced.
